{
  "title": "Gently Spicy Irish Bok Choi Stew",
  "description": "A spicy and velvety Irish stew featuring bok choi and pickle, perfect for a crowd, and satvik-friendly. This dish is a unique blend of flavors and textures.",
  "cuisine": "Irish",
